window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Book 2 in a progression fantasy series perfect for fans of </b><b><i>Dishonored</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>The Blacktongue Thief,</i></b><b> </b><b><i>The Lies of Locke Lamora</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Baldur’s Gate!</i></b><br> <br> <b>About the Series:</b> A slow-burn progression fantasy focused on an Anti-hero MC with a code rising through the criminal underworld of a city-state using newfound powers and quick wits. MC's powers will develop slowly, but he will use them in creative ways to get ahead—and in the meantime, he'll do whatever it takes.</p>"; 
